name: Restless Addicted
description:
This work describes Restlessness as a Symptom of Addiction
restlees is a symptom of addiction that occurs when a person unconsciously becomes uncomfortable with his environment. This is the body's way of responding to things that can result in mental and physical stress. Although anxiety is more common than it seems, there are different conditions in which anxiety can be diagnosed as a symptom.
